nodes.text: Saskia Maarleveld is an audiobook narrator from New Zealand who read the audiobook for the 2017 novel Leia, Princess of Alderaan. Maarleveld also read "Eclipse," a short story in the anthology From a Certain Point of View; "The Wine in Dreams" in the Canto Bight anthology; Most Wanted and Alphabet Squadron.
